data.description: HORSE READY property in Amelia County on 4+ acres features 36'x24' center aisle barn w/3 stalls, tack/feed area, metal roof, hay storage, water, power, RV hook-up & trailer parking. Board & high tensile fence w/ 3 mature pastures, round pen & professionally graded riding arena. Renovated home w/ ONE LEVEL living features 4 bedrooms & 2 full baths w/ solid bamboo & hardwood floors throughout. The spacious family room & living room provide lovely country views. Beautiful updated kitchen open to dining room features hickory cabinets, granite counters, island w/seating, tile backsplash & pantry. Large primary suite has 2 closets & private bath w/ tile floors & tile walk-in shower. Additional exterior features include large deck, solar powered entrance gate w/remote. 20'x11' workshop with 36'x20' overhang has extra storage for vehicles & outdoor equipment. Located in eastern Amelia w/quick access to Rte 360, approx 45 minutes to Richmond, and less than 30 min to shopping, dining & entertainment in Chesterfield County. Enjoy the public riding arena at Joe H. Paulette Memorial Park! Amelia County has LOW tax rate & beautiful rural setting.
